org.aludratest.service.locator.element

Class ElementLocators

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aludratest.service.locator.element.ElementLocators
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<GUIElementLocator>

    public class ElementLocators
extends Object
implements Iterable<GUIElementLocator>
    GUIElementLocator version which wraps a set of alternative GUIElementLocators. To retrieve a GUIElementLocator compatible object, invoke newMutableInstance(). You can (and should) retrieve multiple mutable instances from the same ElementLocators object, as every instance will be modified by the AludraTest framework when the actual element to use is searched and stored in the object.
    Author:
    Marcel Malitz, Volker Bergmann
